name: Sky Striker Ace - Sieg
desc:
2 monsters, including a "Sky Striker Ace" monster
Must be Link Summoned. If this card is Link Summoned: You can target 1 face-up monster on the field; banish it until your opponent's next End Phase. Once per turn: You can target 1 other card you control; this card gains 1000 ATK, then send the targeted card to the GY. You can only Special Summon "Sky Striker Ace - Sieg(s)" once per turn.
str2: Increase ATK and send to GY
